com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.events.map

Class MapShowEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.event.Event
      • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.events.map.MapShowEvent

  • public class MapShowEvent
extends org.bukkit.event.Event
    Event fired when a map becomes shown to a player somewhere. This can be in his own hands, or on an item frame in the world. This event is fired multiple times, whenever a player sees a (new) item frame or opens the map in his hands.
